<p class="header noPspace" dir="ltr">Upcoming Florence Sessions</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr"><strong>Sharing Our Story</strong></p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">Thursday, February 20</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">6:30-8:00pm at Crossroads Florence</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">Have you ever been stumped by a question about your child&rsquo;s past? Or wondered how much you should share? Learn practical skills to &nbsp;communicate our story and respond to questions about our kid&rsquo;s past, in a way that protects and honors them.</p>
